The paper discusses software architecture modeling and variability, which are topics related to software engineering (cs.SE) and product line development (cs.PL). The paper also mentions system evolution, which falls under software development (cs.SD). The use of refactoring techniques is related to software maintenance (cs.LG). Finally, the evaluation of the approach using a case study involves data collection and analysis, which falls under data structures and algorithms (cs.DC).
